Hello <%= "#{@student.firstname} #{@student.lastname}" %>
    <%= "\r\n" %>
      Thank you for your interest in the Michigan Math and Science Scholars! 
      I am happy to report that you have been awarded financial aid in the amount 
      of <%= "#{humanized_money_with_symbol(@finaid.amount)}" %>.
<% unless @balance_due <= 0 %>
<%= "\r\n" %>
      Your remaining balance is <%= "#{humanized_money_with_symbol(@balance_due / 100)}" %>.
<%= "\r\n" %>
      Please log in to your student portal and pay your balance by <%= "#{@finaid.payments_deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y")}" %>
      in order to finalize your enrollment.
<% end %>
<%= "\r\n" %>
      Please ensure that you accept your offer and upload the required documents to your student portal by May 1.
<%= "\r\n" %>
      Congratulations on your achievements in your scholastic studies! 
<%= "\r\n" %>
